= programs =
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	* `Mod-'`										Toggle dropdown terminal (`$TERMINAL`)
	* `Mod-shift-enter`					Launch file browser (vifm)
	* `Mod-w`										Launch web browser (`$BROWSER`)
	* `M-alt-x`									Launch audio/volume system control (pulsemixer) 
	* `M-shitf-w`								Launch wifi manager (nmtui)
	* `M-shift-'`								Toggle dropdown calculator 
	* `M-e`											Launch email client (neomutt)
	* `Mod-m`										Launch music player (ncmpcpp)
	* `Mod-alt-t`								Launch torrent client (transmission-remote-cli)
	* `M-n`											Launch notes (vimwiki)
	* `Mod-alt-e`								Launch emoji picker (script)
	* `M-shitf-n`								Launch RSS feed reader (newsboat )
	* `Mod-r`										Launch resource manager (bashtop)
	* `Mod-shift-r`							Launch resource manager (htop)
	* `Mod-alt-s`								Toggle screenkey

